data.description: Rare opportunity in desirable Harrisburg! This fully updated brick home sits on nearly one acre. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, solid surface countertops, new cabinetry, and modern light fixtures. Granite composite sink with a garbage disposal.  Stunning engineered hardwood flooring span the entire house, creating a seamless and elegant look. Smart switches compatible with Alexa throughout (excluding bathrooms).  Key updates include a new roof & HVAC system within the last 3 years, with bi-annual maintenance to the HVAC. Both bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled, boasting tile walk-in showers, new vanities, and stylish tile floors.  The backyard is fully fenced with a large deck perfect for outdoor entertaining. Dive into fun with an above-ground pool.  Explore your green thumb in raised beds and blueberry, blackberry, raspberry, and mulberry plants.  Don't miss the chance to own this turnkey property that blends modern amenities with timeless charm.
